'''Domain Hul''' was a [[domain]] among the [[warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Domain Hul was a very powerful Domain, so much that it had [[Domain Hul worldship|its own]] [[Koros-Strohna|worldship]]. Many warriors of Domain Hul took part in the [[Battle of Borleias (Yuuzhan Vong War; Second)|Battle of Borleias]], where their worldship was lost.

